dct_description_sm: Base map of Sussex County. Plate 5 of a six plate map. Prepared by the New Jersey State Highway Department, Division of Planning in cooperation with the U. S. Department of Commerce, Bureau of Public Roads. Culture, county roads and municipal streets are as of 1940.
